550
00:43:45,894 --> 00:43:47,455
(T'road Airline Business Plan)

551
00:43:50,501 --> 00:43:51,463
Now, then...

552
00:43:53,379 --> 00:43:55,238
Let's start our overdue meeting.

553
00:44:10,622 --> 00:44:11,697
Hey.

554
00:44:12,081 --> 00:44:13,113
How have you been doing?

555
00:44:13,477 --> 00:44:14,432
Not good.

556
00:44:14,592 --> 00:44:15,813
Do you think I'll be doing well?

557
00:44:16,363 --> 00:44:18,953
